(3, NULL, 'BANG BAO BEACH', '<div class=\"beach__body\">\n							<div class=\"beach__about\">\n								<p class=\"beach__about-title\" style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\">\n									THAILAND\'S OVERLOOKED, LAID-BACK PARADISE								</p>\n								<p class=\"beach__about-text\">\n									With increasing tourism in Thailand, the island of Koh Kood seems to still remain quiet avoiding big crowds making its beaches like Bang Bao Beach remain quiet and pristine. Bang Bao Beach has all the elements of a perfect Thai beach, framed by lush jungle and very clear, shallow waters ideal for swimming and just an overall laid-back atmosphere. What also makes Bang Bao Beach unique is its charming fishing village, where visitors can stroll along a wooden pier and enjoy fresh seafood at local restaurants. The surrounding area is rich in natural beauty instead of big tourist development but instead stunning views of the Gulf of Thailand and nearby islands. 	\n								</p>\n							</div>\n							<div class=\"beach__image\">\n								<img src=\"https://worlds50beaches.com/assets/images/maps/map-2025-03.jpg\" alt=\"map\">\n							</div>\n						</div>\n					</div>\n\n', '<div class=\"container\"> 					<div class=\"more\"> 						<div class=\"more__item\"> 							<p class=\"more__item-title\" style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\"> 								Bang Bao Beach WEATHER AVERAGES 							</p> 							<table class=\"weather__table\"> 								<thead> 									<tr> 										<td class=\"first__cell\"></td> 										<td>AVG. HIGH</td> 										<td>AVG. LOW</td> 										<td>RAINY DAYS</td> 									</tr> 								</thead> 								<tbody> 									<tr> 										<td class=\"first__cell\">JANUARY</td> 										<td> 											<span>30</span> 											° 										</td> 										<td> 											<span>25</span> 											° 										</td> 										<td>2.9</td> 									</tr> 									<tr> 										<td class=\"first__cell\">FEBRUARY</td> 										<td> 											<span>30</span> 											° 										