(18, NULL, 'PLAYA DE RODAS', '<div class=\"beach__body\">\n							<div class=\"beach__about\">\n								<p class=\"beach__about-title\" style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\">\n									A CARIBBEAN PARADISE HIDDEN IN EUROPE								</p>\n								<p class=\"beach__about-text\">\n									Playa de Rodas is a gently curved beach about 700 meters long, located in the Cíes Islands off the coast of Galicia, Spain. This stunning beach is often hailed as one of Europe’s most beautiful, featuring soft white sand and clear, calm waters. Many refer to Playa de Rodas as a Caribbean-like paradise, but with the cool, refreshing waters of the Atlantic. The surroundings are equally breathtaking, with the beach backed by lush pine forests and sand dunes. The only way to reach it is by boat, ensuring a tranquil escape where visitors can swim, sunbathe, or explore the surrounding trails without large crowds.	\n								</p>\n							</div>\n							<div class=\"beach__image\">\n								<img src=\"https://worlds50beaches.com/assets/images/maps/map-2025-18.jpg\" alt=\"map\">\n							</div>\n						</div>\n', ' <div class=\"container\"> 					<div class=\"more\"> 						<div class=\"more__item\"> 							<p class=\"more__item-title\" style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\"> 								Playa de Rodas WEATHER AVERAGES 							</p> 							<table class=\"weather__table\"> 								<thead> 									<tr> 										<td class=\"first__cell\"></td> 										<td>AVG. HIGH</td> 										<td>AVG. LOW</td> 										<td>RAINY DAYS</td> 									</tr> 								</thead> 								<tbody> 									<tr> 										<td class=\"first__cell\">JANUARY</td> 										<td> 											<span>13</span> 											° 										</td> 										<td> 											<span>8</span> 											° 										</td> 										<td>11.9</td> 									</tr> 									<tr> 										<td class=\"first__cell\">FEBRUARY</td> 										<td> 											<span>14</span> 											° 										</td> 										<td> 											<span>8</span> 											° 									