(19, NULL, 'PLAYA BALANDRA', '<div class=\"beach__body\">\n							<div class=\"beach__about\">\n								<p class=\"beach__about-title\" style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\">\n									MEXICO\'S OFF THE BEATEN PATH GEM								</p>\n								<p class=\"beach__about-text\">\n									Despite its popularity, Playa Balandra in La Paz retains its incredible untouched beauty thanks to strict regulations that limit development, the number of visitors, and activities that could disrupt its natural state. As part of a protected natural area, the beach remains clean and unspoiled, offering visitors a stunning beach experience. The area is renowned for its shallow, calm waters and the distinctive mushroom-shaped rock formation known as \'El Hongo.\' The shallow waters across the entire bay make it particularly appealing for families and those looking to unwind. The bay is composed of seven beaches, and because the tides never rise above chest height, visitors can often walk around and explore each one—providing a truly unique experience.	\n								</p>\n							</div>\n							<div class=\"beach__image\">\n								<img src=\"https://worlds50beaches.com/assets/images/maps/map-2025-19.jpg\" alt=\"map\">\n							</div>\n						</div>\n', ' <div class=\"container\"> 					<div class=\"more\"> 						<div class=\"more__item\"> 							<p class=\"more__item-title\" style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\"> 								Playa Balandra WEATHER AVERAGES 							</p> 							<table class=\"weather__table\"> 								<thead> 									<tr> 										<td class=\"first__cell\"></td> 										<td>AVG. HIGH</td> 										<td>AVG. LOW</td> 										<td>RAINY DAYS</td> 									</tr> 								</thead> 								<tbody> 									<tr> 										<td class=\"first__cell\">JANUARY</td> 										<td> 											<span>24</span> 											° 										</td> 										<td> 											<span>12</span> 											° 										</td> 										<td>1.5</td> 									</tr> 									<tr> 										<td class=\"first__cell\">FEBRUAR