(22, NULL, 'PLAYA PUNTA UVA', '<div class=\"beach__body\">\n							<div class=\"beach__about\">\n								<p class=\"beach__about-title\" style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\">\n									UNTOUCHED BEAUTY AND TROPICAL WILDLIFE								</p>\n								<p class=\"beach__about-text\">\n									At Playa Punta Uva in Costa Rica, white sand meets lush rainforest, creating a breathtaking blend of natural beauty and tranquility. Just outside Puerto Viejo, this idyllic spot is perfect for swimming and surfing, with vibrant coral reefs teeming with marine life just offshore. Towering palms and dense jungle provide shade, while sloths, monkeys, and colorful toucans add to the enchanting atmosphere. With its secluded, untouched beauty and peaceful ambiance, Punta Uva isn’t just a beach—it’s an escape into nature’s paradise.	\n								</p>\n							</div>\n							<div class=\"beach__image\">\n								<img src=\"https://worlds50beaches.com/assets/images/maps/map-2025-41.jpg\" alt=\"map\">\n							</div>\n						</div>\n', ' <div class=\"container\"> 					<div class=\"more\"> 						<div class=\"more__item\"> 							<p class=\"more__item-title\" style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\"> 								Playa Punta Uva WEATHER AVERAGES 							</p> 							<table class=\"weather__table\"> 								<thead> 									<tr> 										<td class=\"first__cell\"></td> 										<td>AVG. HIGH</td> 										<td>AVG. LOW</td> 										<td>RAINY DAYS</td> 									</tr> 								</thead> 								<tbody> 									<tr> 										<td class=\"first__cell\">JANUARY</td> 										<td> 											<span>29</span> 											° 										</td> 										<td> 											<span>25</span> 											° 										</td> 										<td>5.5</td> 									</tr> 									<tr> 										<td class=\"first__cell\">FEBRUARY</td> 										<td> 											<span>29</span> 											° 										</td> 										<td> 											<span>24</span> 											° 										</td> 										<td>4</td> 									</tr> 									<tr> 										<td class=\"