(32, NULL, 'THE BATHS', '<div class=\"beach__body\">\n                                                        <div class=\"beach__about\">\n                                                                <p class=\"beach__about-title\" style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\">\n                                                                        A UNIQUE, OTHERWORLDLY CARIBBEAN BEACH                                                                </p>\n                                                                <p class=\"beach__about-text\">\n                                                                        The Baths, located on Virgin Gorda in the British Virgin Islands, is one of the most unique and breathtaking beaches in the Caribbean. What sets this beach apart are its stunning natural rock formations—giant granite boulders scattered across the shoreline, creating hidden caves, tide pools, and grottoes that invite exploration. The crystal-clear waters surrounding the rocks are often calm, making it the perfect place to swim and relax. The soft, white sand stretches along the beach, and visitors can navigate through the rock labyrinths, discovering secret spots and secluded coves. The Baths offers an otherworldly and more unique experience, making it an adventurous and must-see destination.        \n                                                                </p>\n                                                        </div>\n                                                        <div class=\"beach__image\">\n                                                                <img src=\"https://worlds50beaches.com/assets/images/maps/map-2025-29.jpg\" alt=\"map\">\n                                                        </div>\n                                                </div>', ' <div class=\"container\">                                         <div class=\"more\">                                                 <div class=\"more__item\">        