(34, NULL, 'KLEIN BONAIRE BEACH', '<div class=\"beach__body\">\n                                                        <div class=\"beach__about\">\n                                                                <p class=\"beach__about-title\" style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\">\n                                                                        A BEAUTIFUL, UNINHABITED CARIBBEAN SECRET                                                                </p>\n                                                                <p class=\"beach__about-text\">\n                                                                        Klein Bonaire Beach, located just off the coast of Bonaire in the Caribbean, is an uninhabited, pristine island offering a truly unique and secluded beach experience. While often overlooked in favor of more popular Caribbean destinations, Bonaire—and particularly Klein Bonaire—stands out. With no resorts or buildings on the island, it serves as a peaceful sanctuary for nature lovers and those seeking a tranquil, off-the-beaten-path beach experience. The landscape remains untouched, and the waters are exceptionally clear. Bonaire is renowned as one of the world’s top diving destinations, and Klein Bonaire shares in this reputation, having a vibrant marine life just offshore. Easily accessible by boat from Bonaire, Klein Bonaire provides visitors with a serene escape far removed from the crowds.        \n                                                                </p>\n                                                        </div>\n                                                        <div class=\"beach__image\">\n                                                                <img src=\"https://worlds50beaches.com/assets/images/maps/map-2025-44.jpg\" alt=\"map\">\n                                                        </div>\n                                                </div>\n', ' <div class=\"container\">                         