(46, NULL, 'GOYAMBOKKA BEACH', '<div class=\"beach__body\">\n                                                        <div class=\"beach__about\">\n                                                                <p class=\"beach__about-title\" style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\">\n                                                                        ICONIC GOLDEN SAND BEACH IN SRI LANKA                                                                </p>\n                                                                <p class=\"beach__about-text\">\n                                                                        Goyambokka Beach has all the features of a perfect Sri Lankan beach. Located near Tangalle on the southern coast of Sri Lanka, it’s a bit farther from the airport, ensuring a calmer, less crowded atmosphere. The golden sand and tall, slender palm trees are iconic elements of Sri Lankan beaches, and Goyambokka is a prime example of this. With only a few laid-back establishments along the beach, it remains unspoiled and peaceful, offering a great spot to relax for an entire day. The small inlet has strong waves, making it ideal for bodysurfing and catching waves. It’s also a fantastic place to witness one of Sri Lanka\'s iconic sunsets, with a backdrop of perfect palm trees.        \n                                                                </p>\n                                                        </div>\n                                                        <div class=\"beach__image\">\n                                                                <img src=\"https://worlds50beaches.com/assets/images/maps/map-2025-40.jpg\" alt=\"map\">\n                                                        </div>\n                                                </div>', ' <div class=\"container\">                                         <div class=\"more\">                                                 <div class=\"more__item\">                     