                                       <p>                                                                                         High season peaks in July and August, and La Pelosa is much busier during those months than it is at other times of the year. June and September are a great compromise with less crowds and excellent weather.                                                                                </p>                                                                         </li>                                                                         <li>                                                                                 <p><b>CALM SEAS</b></p>                                                                                 <p>                                                                                         The Mediterranean is much calmer from June through October, which is the best time of year to visit La Pelosa.                                                                                </p>                                                                         </li>                                                                         <li>                                                                                 <p><b>TIME OF DAY</b></p>                                                                                 <p>                                                                                         Due to the popularity of European beaches in summer, we recommend visiting La Pelosa fairly early in the morning to enjoy it without it being very crowded.                                                                                </p>                                                                         </li>                                                                 </ul>                                                         </div>                                                 </div>             